com.i2group.apollo.securityapi
Interface IPrincipalProvider

All Known Implementing Classes:
WebSphereRoleBasedPrincipalProvider
public interface IPrincipalProvider

A provider of information about a Principal, including its "access" and "grant" rights.

This is used to inform the system about who the current user, is and what they are permitted to do.

Since:
1.0
